ng. Piper Jaffray maintained the stock with "Overweight" rating in Monday, November 2 report. The firm earned "Buy" rating on Friday, July 22 by Stifel Nicolaus. The rating was initiated by UBS with "Buy" on Wednesday, December 16.Market Capitalization can be thought of as the overall price to buy the company. The stock has "Outperform" rating by RBC Capital Markets on Thursday, April 27.





